OL,3,CDumfries and Galloway population falls
OL,4,Cas Scotland's grows
OL,6,FThe population in Dumfries and
OL,7,FGalloway is declining, bucking the
OL,8,Fnational trend of a growing national
OL,9,Fpopulation in Scotland.
OL,11,FThe report released by the National
OL,12,FRecord of Scotland showcased how the
OL,13,Fpopulation dropped to just over
OL,14,F145,000 in 2023 in Dumfries and
OL,15,FGalloway.
OL,17,FNational population levels for
OL,18,FScotland showcased that the number of
OL,19,Fpeople living in the country rose at
OL,20,Fthe fastest level since the 1940s.
