OL,3,CDumfries and Galloway population falls
OL,4,Cas Scotland's grows
OL,6,FThe figures show that the population
OL,7,Ffor Scotland is just under 5.5
OL,8,Fmillion, having risen by 43,000 from
OL,9,F2022.
OL,11,FDumfries and Galloway is one of seven
OL,12,Flocal authorities in Scotland to see
OL,13,Ftheir population fall.
OL,15,FSouth Scotland MSP Colin Smyth said:
OL,16,F"It is of little surprise that the
OL,17,Fareas showing a drop in population
OL,18,Fover the past year are predominantly
OL,19,Fisland or rural communities.
