OL,3,CDumfries and Galloway population falls
OL,4,Cas Scotland's grows
OL,6,F"Our region, like many other parts of
OL,7,FScotland, has an ageing population.
OL,8,FHowever, this isn't just because many
OL,9,Folder people retire in our region, but
OL,10,Fshamefully because we have the biggest
OL,11,Foutward migration of young people in
OL,12,Fthe country.
OL,14,F"Far too many of our young people are
OL,15,Fleaving their towns and villages for
OL,16,Fthe high-skill, high-wage employment
OL,17,Fopportunities that are not always
OL,18,Favailable in Dumfries and Galloway.
