OL,3,CDumfries and Galloway population falls
OL,4,Cas Scotland's grows
OL,6,F"As we can see in some recent debates
OL,7,Flocally, too many people simply do not
OL,8,Fwant change in our region even
OL,9,Falthough it is clear the economic
OL,10,Fmodel is broken. But if we do not grab
OL,11,Fthe economic opportunities for our
OL,12,Fregion, our population will continue
OL,13,Fto fall."
